Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.82,0:00:35.68,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,將軍事化的非人類組織起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:42.05,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,毀滅人類社會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:48.64,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,不剩一人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.22,0:01:02.15,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1070.4,625)}仔細地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:01:02.15,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(774.4,626.6)}一絲不苟地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:01:02.15,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(496,626.6)}確認
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.26,0:01:02.15,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(235.2,629.8)}反覆確認
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:04.70,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(940.8,588.2)}仔細尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:08.53,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}一個人都不剩地將地面上的人全部殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:13.41,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,毀滅人類讓新生物接管世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.03,0:01:19.08,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠持續的美好的暗黑時代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:24.80,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,故此我的名字就叫做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.21,0:01:30.18,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,「黑王」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.39,0:01:47.07,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,威爾利那巷戰之後幾天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:57.36,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(445.333,197)\fad(350,500)}The Outlandish Knight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:57.36,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(180,106.334)\fad(350,500)}第十五幕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.66,0:01:53.02,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,交易成立
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.57,0:01:55.41,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,就把糧食還有資金借給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:57.62,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,利息一點也不能少
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:01:59.93,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王要攻打過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:03.15,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前不得不讓衰弱的奧爾特振興起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:05.65,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了嗎 聖日耳曼伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:08.97,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,已經得到承諾了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:11.19,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,還真能幹呢 那個人妖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:12.33,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:14.71,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,公主大人太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.13,0:02:16.59,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說 聖日耳曼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:19.14,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡偷窺的都是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.21,0:02:21.59,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,是漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:24.04,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,織田信長和那須與一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:26.97,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的還有漢尼拔巴卡老爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:30.73,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,還有總大將的島津豐久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:32.55,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,然後還有你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:34.89,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,奧爾特真是狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:37.88,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流者一個接一個地漂流到那邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:40.07,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,你就沒有感覺到有一股意志嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:41.76,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,來自某人的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:44.09,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,那也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:47.00,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我們輸了的話 所有都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:48.43,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,包括這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:50.42,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:52.20,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,大方地援助我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:54.70,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,殷勤招待我們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.79,0:02:57.55,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們吃好的用好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:03:02.15,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,幫助我們儘快振興這個疲憊的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:04.26,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真是說了些有趣的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.79,0:03:08.92,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我覺得只是給予你們援助就太無聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:11.23,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來做生意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:14.36,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,奧爾特有精靈對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:17.19,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,那個很美麗的人種
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:19.37,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 的確是有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.43,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,但你在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.04,0:03:25.90,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,很多古彬連的有錢人都喜歡精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:27.14,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:29.92,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你想說讓我們販賣精靈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:33.36,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,讓精靈女性穿著可愛的制服在劇院裡面唱歌跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:38.32,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,為之傾心的年輕人就會大把大把地購買周邊商品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:41.16,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,和精靈的握手會之類的應該能狠狠地賺一筆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:42.11,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,這個可以有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:44.22,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事情當然是不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:46.66,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,讓精靈進行接待的酒吧麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:48.21,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,這個可以有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:48.97,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:52.92,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,讓精靈的男性來接待富婆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:54.04,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,這個也可以有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:55.25,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:04:01.70,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎來到安土城男公關部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:04.46,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是這裡的負責人織田信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:08.11,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？費用太高了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:11.57,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就稍微來一下裡面的事務所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:14.41,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦不妙啊 好適合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:16.68,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,有點像真島的哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:17.73,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:20.08,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝你的指名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:22.81,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,在下的源氏名是與一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:24.57,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,源氏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:27.73,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,幫我取得店內營業額排名第一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:30.36,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 喝吧喝吧喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:32.07,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.41,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,大把大把地揮霍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:35.10,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,大把大把地揮霍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:38.80,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,熱情已經在想像中高漲了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.10,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:45.17,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我也總有一天會在威爾利那二丁目開店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:48.28,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集著熟客的我的小店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:49.76,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一點啊 人妖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:51.61,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,快回到現實中來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.15,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,是我們錯了 人妖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:28.31,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(69.334,261)}奧爾特北部 山脈森林地帶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:32.17,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我們和奧爾特的戰鬥連戰連勝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:35.71,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,這都是因為天空神大人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:40.14,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,然後現在又有新的力量要加入我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:42.83,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是貓族一伙人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:47.48,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是為了和奧爾特戰鬥而集結起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:50.46,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我覺得你們犬人所說的天空神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:54.89,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,首先得好好證明他是否有資格當我們的頭領
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:56.84,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,你這隻貓在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.05,0:06:58.90,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是對天空神大人的無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:02.95,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我一開始就不怎麼願意和你們這些狗輩一起戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:06.65,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,然後你們還將舉止如此隨便的東西稱為神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:09.69,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 起來啊神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:11.25,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,他們正在說你呢 神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:13.59,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,話說這個椅子是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:17.89,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,看吶 這個樣子也算是神嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.07,0:07:20.79,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,在重要的結盟會議上睡迷糊了的神？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.01,0:07:22.59,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才說你們這些狗輩們真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:40.55,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:42.93,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,貓族第一的勇將阿梅傑居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:44.07,Drifters More,,0,0,0,,是魔術嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:44.82,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.26,0:07:48.22,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,貓啊 果然是貓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:54.73,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,貓族全部都跪拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:57.20,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,是神 這是神的技藝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:08:00.47,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是貓呢 果然是貓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.64,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,是動物王國麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:04.96,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,貓咪貓咪貓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:07.93,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,西庇阿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:10.55,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你說話應該是最快捷明瞭的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:13.78,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,是來自十月機關的聯絡 還很緊急
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:18.60,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王的軍隊終於要向南面前進了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:22.26,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕北方諸國會被陸續毀滅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:25.15,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦開始了就不會停止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:27.72,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,來到這裡也只是時間的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:34.25,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,在「北壁」所見的規模甚至算不上軍隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:36.54,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,不 規模根本沒得比
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:40.59,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候的兵力就已經把北壁打成那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:42.04,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,可以立即告訴你答案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:43.06,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:47.54,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的我們是不能和那種移動災厄戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:50.91,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,南面的國家 奧爾特已經被漂流者所奪取
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:54.02,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,現在那裡正不斷地集結著漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.95,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,戰事一旦打響…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:57.73,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 玻利維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:09:00.02,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,過得還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:04.35,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈 是的 玻利維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:06.92,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我有信帶給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:08.96,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,信麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:19.76,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,致於北方之地的日本飛行員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:23.90,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我從與我接觸的自稱十月機關的人口中聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:26.88,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,有人說著日語駕駛著飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:28.66,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,這封信就是為了求證這個事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:34.03,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我是大日本帝國海軍少將 山口多聞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:39.96,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在在南方的叫古彬連的商業島國的岩礁之上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:47.37,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在和嚴重損害並觸了礁的航空母艦「飛龍」一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:50.12,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有回信的意願
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:53.80,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,就把這封信還給送信的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:09:59.41,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:06.46,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,你還活著啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:12.42,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,你這「行兇者多聞丸」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:16.05,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,要來了 要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:18.03,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,終於要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:21.19,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,他們已經在北壁建立了根據地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:22.89,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,那是魔物的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:26.96,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面的狀況正如弦上之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:28.96,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,弓已經拉滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:32.33,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,北壁的門再次打開的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:33.66,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,會一口氣涌過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:35.66,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,就像山崩一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:38.20,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,緊急往各個國家派遣使者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:41.38,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王廢滅世界的長征要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:44.56,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,南伐 南伐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:46.97,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,長征之時已到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:49.87,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,是時候要參與根絕人類的旅途了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:52.04,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,廢棄世界之時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:53.83,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,廢棄人類之時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:57.57,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王的大名將在天地間響徹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:01.69,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,打開大門
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:07.19,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,將人類世界變成非人世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:27.41,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,惟任光秀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:31.53,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,半人馬的騎兵我就拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:34.51,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我放開手幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:37.54,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我信得過你的才幹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:39.90,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,就像源平合戰那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:44.41,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,如同風火般迅速擾亂敵方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:48.53,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,先頭部隊的大將由土方閣下擔當
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:51.72,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,應敵之策就由你定奪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:55.56,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,不用理會後方的本陣 盡情上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:59.82,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,但是請絕對不要強攻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:01.91,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,土方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:04.06,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,不要出現傷兵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:06.77,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,因為黑王大人會將他們全部都治好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:08.39,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,一個不剩地全部治好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:10.22,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是多麼弱的兵也好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.49,0:12:14.57,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,但是相應地也會讓黑王大人使用力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:19.25,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,所以有兵負傷但存活下來的話 乾脆讓他死去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:24.81,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,阿納斯塔西婭皇女殿下就在後方陣地待命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:27.54,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,會在合適的時機讓你上場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:32.62,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,戰爭 不是太喜歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:34.07,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,因為好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:38.79,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,你還不太懂自己的力量的使用方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:42.74,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,根據使用的方法甚至能夠扭轉戰局
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:44.00,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斯普京殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:46.41,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,分化敵人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:47.54,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:50.72,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,即使沒有內應但至少應該會互相猜疑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:57.33,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,最後都會把人類一個不剩地殺掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.66,0:13:00.22,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,他們還有人會通敵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:02.54,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,當然會有 皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:05.16,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,人是種在被處刑之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:07.95,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,會想著只有自己能得救就好了的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:10.89,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,然後會為了延後自己被處刑的順序
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:15.18,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,而出賣別人來討好處刑人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:19.54,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,這種痛苦你不是也切身體會過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:22.63,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:27.33,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,惟任 我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:29.91,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,傷已經好了嗎 貞德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:30.65,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,少廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:32.70,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我去把漂流者給燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:35.18,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我去把那個島津豐久給燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:38.83,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,只有那傢伙 我要親手把他燒死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:42.22,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要把他燒得灰都不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:44.77,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:49.29,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:51.30,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,請向我下令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.75,0:13:52.54,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,燒了他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:54.40,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,燒死他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:58.09,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,會燒 會讓你燒的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:00.37,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,所以先待命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:08.48,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,惟任 發動戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:09.93,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,蹂躪他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:13.62,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,從北方的凍土到南方的北壁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:17.08,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,從西方的荒漠到東方的大海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:21.55,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,下至未出生的胎兒上到臨終的老人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:23.81,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人都不留
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:25.43,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,仔細地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:26.47,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,一絲不苟地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.18,0:14:28.25,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,確認
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:30.15,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,反覆確認
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.27,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,仔細尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:36.13,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,無差別地 精心地將一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:41.17,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,將地面上的人一個不留地全部殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:47.20,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,開始進軍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:03.63,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,給我等著 信長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:08.90,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,你這蠢貨 死了才好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:15.50,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(88,179.667)}「北壁」的南方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:15.50,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(138.667,277)}拉·茲納酋長國境
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:15.46,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的 他們真的開始向南進軍了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:18.47,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,正如十月機關那些傢伙所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:20.31,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,發生大事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:22.88,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,立即召集各氏族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:24.74,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,要趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:27.02,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 但是啊 酋長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:32.59,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,要 要和那種東西戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:39.69,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道北方部族的國家能夠拖延多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:44.00,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,他們在北壁淪陷之後也一直在戒備著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.09,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,拖延不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:50.00,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,他們會像浸濕的紙被刺穿一樣全數被滅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:53.02,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,結果正如那個叫信長的人所說的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:57.04,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有任何一個人把自己的軍隊交給漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:16:00.64,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,無論我們怎麼向他們訴說黑王軍的威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:03.94,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,蹂躪他們 蹂躪他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:05.46,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,進行革新
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:07.79,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,重建世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.46,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,弓箭沒用 會被彈開的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:30.44,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還有狗頭人騎在背上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:33.12,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼巨人族會穿著鎧甲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:36.27,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼巨人族會和狗頭人互相協助啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:54.44,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,全身覆蓋青銅鎧的巨人在立於部隊前方蹂躪敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:58.56,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,騎在背上的狗頭人和哥布林則警戒著周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.62,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,指揮巨人 支援巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:05.00,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,由巨人進行運送並壓制敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.51,0:17:06.40,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,註：танковый десант(tankovyy desant)，即戰車跨乘或稱為步坦協同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.51,0:17:06.40,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,「步坦協同」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:10.72,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道居然有這種戰鬥方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:18.49,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是飛龍從空中的支援
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:21.99,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,還是空降士兵的戰鬥方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:26.46,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王為什麼會知道這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:31.82,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,他真的是我所想的「那個」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:34.76,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:37.15,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,無論他是誰還是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:40.12,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠殺死信長的話也就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:04.21,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,隨便殺殺就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:06.11,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,把恐怖埋入他們的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:09.26,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,為了逃避災難而向鄰國逃跑的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:11.99,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,難民就會占滿鄰國城市的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:17.03,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來就不能隨心所欲地召集和調動軍隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:20.53,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,難民也要吃飯拉屎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:24.27,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼請變得越來越難受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:27.28,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,變得越來越容易淪陷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:35.05,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,把你們所有人都燒起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:37.73,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是漂流者所占據的奧爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.91,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會給他們的巷道帶來火焰與灰燼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:47.89,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德這傢伙真是讓人頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:49.29,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,亂燒一通
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:52.50,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,人類可是重要的資源啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:55.07,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,不要隨便對待人類的屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:57.80,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,要非常珍重地對待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:01.97,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,要稍微減輕一下黑王大人的負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:05.20,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,頭髮可以用來做火絨和繩子還有細繩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:06.69,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,肉是食物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:08.03,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,血是飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:11.13,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,皮用來做衣服和皮製品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:12.93,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,骨頭用來做裝飾品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:15.88,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,「人類渾身上下都是寶」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:29.52,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:31.62,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我的心沸騰不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.41,0:19:34.70,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是在這種不知道哪裡的巷道也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:37.52,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,這應該是我所期待的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:39.56,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該是個渴戰鬼才對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:42.08,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是最喜歡戰爭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:43.91,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:50.01,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我的確非常享受和那個混賬白痴的對毆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:19:54.23,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:56.00,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.28,0:19:57.70,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個城市
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:59.36,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個堡壘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:00.92,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,尖塔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:03.58,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,就像割草一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:05.56,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,就像拍打白蟻一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:08.14,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,就像去除小石頭一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:11.96,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,向著下一個地方前進
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:17.18,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,贏不了 我們的軍隊贏不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.02,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,集結殘餘兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.91,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,向南 向奧爾特前進
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:27.34,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界的軍隊絕對贏不了那些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:29.48,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:32.62,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,能打倒不屬於這個世界的生物的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:35.17,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,也就只有不屬於這個世界的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:52.86,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,把韁繩給我 混賬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.78,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,都跟你說過不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:20:56.18,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我操縱它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:20:59.43,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,在天上飛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:01.72,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,已經到了 西庇阿大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:05.80,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.44,0:21:08.66,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:11.35,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,是「多聞丸」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.05,0:21:17.06,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第三四三海軍航空隊 戰鬥第三〇一飛行隊新選組隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:19.45,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,菅野直大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:21.78,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我僭越 山口少將
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:23.72,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,請先和我相撲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:30.04,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,你本應該在中途島就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.30,0:21:32.07,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,你說不定是個亡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:34.07,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,所以讓我來把你摔一次試試
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:35.96,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 菅野大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:37.77,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我不認識你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:41.14,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,大尉 你是什麼時候被送到這裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:44.75,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,1945年8月1日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.34,0:21:47.93,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,天空神大人在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:50.58,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:54.87,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,是蠻族之間的風俗習慣之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:56.89,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,日本怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:22:00.91,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,反正下場肯定很糟糕吧 大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:06.33,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,居然不問輸贏之類的 不愧是你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.11,0:22:09.50,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,在本來就沒有勝算的那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:14.40,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟王牌的航空戰隊在我的眼前消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:25.74,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,全都如同灰燼一般了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.42,0:22:29.95,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,聯合艦隊都被摧毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:32.78,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:36.18,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是大和還是武藏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.30,0:22:39.14,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,都已經成為海中的碎屑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.44,0:22:43.54,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我來這邊的時間並不長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.47,0:22:46.45,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,聯合艦隊還沒有被毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.19,0:22:48.60,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,飛龍還在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:53.29,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,而且這裡還有提督以及飛行員
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.00,0:22:55.35,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然只有兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.03,0:22:57.35,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們就是二航戰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.99,0:23:02.23,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,九九式艦載轟炸機
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.38,0:23:03.34,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,九七式艦上攻擊機
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:05.82,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,零式艦載戰鬥機21型
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.49,0:23:07.97,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是破損的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:10.49,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有一台正常的飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.23,0:23:12.91,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,但也不是沒可能
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.63,0:23:15.07,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,炸彈和燃料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.65,0:23:17.35,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,幾乎都沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.28,0:23:20.71,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,但還有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.61,0:23:25.44,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然分量不足以滿足曾經的航空戰隊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.85,0:23:27.09,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在這種場合
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.39,0:23:29.76,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,不 以這個世界的情況來說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.68,0:23:32.77,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只有能在天上飛的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.10,0:23:35.34,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,也會是足以逆轉局勢的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.76,0:23:39.41,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,不過啊 這是真的飛龍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.78,0:23:41.28,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,其他船員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.86,0:23:42.71,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.28,0:23:46.80,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,來到這邊的時候 艦上就只有我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.86,0:23:49.90,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,連屍體都沒有一具
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.16,0:23:51.74,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.28,0:23:55.31,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊那個像是在羅馬歌劇裡面出來的人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.68,0:23:58.77,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 可能意大利亞的藝人之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.88,0:23:59.66,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.76,0:24:01.54,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我是西庇阿·阿非利加努斯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.83,0:24:05.07,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的西庇阿是那個西庇阿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.59,0:24:06.64,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,布匿戰爭的那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.18,0:24:07.98,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.10,0:24:10.40,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,西庇阿 是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.67,0:24:13.16,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,話說我還是第一次聽到你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.29,0:24:16.05,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,既然說是羅馬就給我帶個凱撒大帝來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.13,0:24:17.59,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過很多次了！很多次了！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.68,0:24:20.21,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個野蠻人真是討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.39,0:24:23.26,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,話說這個鋼鐵之城是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.54,0:24:27.83,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,而且這個鐵塊就是在北壁之上飛行的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.51,0:24:30.59,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是城池而是船
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.18,0:24:32.26,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做航空母艦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.59,0:24:34.76,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,航空母…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.05,0:24:38.17,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？這是船？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.28,0:24:40.02,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我有東西想給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.81,0:24:41.56,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,請到這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.03,0:24:46.54,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,大尉 你雖然是航空兵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.02,0:24:49.65,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,但只要是海軍的士官都應該知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.63,0:24:54.21,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然幾乎都被水浸濕了或被炸飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.42,0:24:57.63,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,因為原本的數量比較多 所以有少許能用的裝備還剩下來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.42,0:25:02.64,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我們海軍有在艦內準備能讓船員在突發時
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.80,0:25:08.28,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,編組一支陸戰隊的裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.06,0:25:11.31,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.66,0:25:15.08,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是有的嘛 畢竟是飛龍
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.50,0:25:18.24,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小狗狗 試試拿著這個
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.55,0:25:20.11,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,請住手 天空神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.38,0:25:21.46,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.71,0:25:22.79,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.12,0:25:24.57,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,這次又是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.91,0:25:25.51,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,槍
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.84,0:25:26.69,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,步槍
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.94,0:25:29.00,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,西庇阿先生
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.37,0:25:31.37,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你真的是西庇阿
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.25,0:25:36.09,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 這裡是有來自遙遠未來的武器的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.63,0:25:38.34,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,遙遠未來？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.87,0:25:41.81,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,因為和迦太基的戰爭是發生在公元前的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.16,0:25:45.50,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,這是大約兩千年以後的未來的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.86,0:25:47.66,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,兩…兩千
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.59,0:25:52.23,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,提督快看看這個 快看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.43,0:25:54.21,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,「野狗黑吉」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.43,0:25:54.21,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,註：「野狗黑吉」，出自「のらくろ放浪記」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.35,0:25:55.82,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,有隻「野狗黑吉」在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.95,0:25:58.31,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人不是穿人偶服的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.49,0:26:01.54,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 「野狗黑吉」二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.80,0:26:03.55,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,提督
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.32,0:26:06.06,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,請把這兩千年來的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.34,0:26:09.72,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,大概也行 能不能告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.17,0:26:14.92,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,特別是這兩千年發展起來的軍事方面的技術 武器
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.13,0:26:16.33,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,思考 思想
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.56,0:26:18.24,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,戰術 革新
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.04,0:26:20.70,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,僅你所知也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.90,0:26:22.64,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.32,0:26:25.65,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是一介海軍軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.11,0:26:29.39,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,只能告訴你一些零碎的 大體的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.74,0:26:30.83,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.12,0:26:32.67,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我會自己理解
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.98,0:26:34.47,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我很擅長學習
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.80,0:26:36.56,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,我連漢尼拔也追得上了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.00,0:26:40.17,Drifters More,NTP,0,0,0,,這次就讓我來試著追趕這兩千年的發展
